msgid "This utility should only be used in live mode!"
msgstr "Perkakas ini hanya boleh digunakan dalam mode langsung!"

msgid ""
"<span font='12'>This tool should be used in live mode and to restore the Manjaro boot\n"
"installed on HD or SSD.</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='12' foreground='red'>If the installed system is starting correctly there are no "
"problems in the boot, so it is\n"
"better not to continue the use of this tool.</span>\n"
"<span font='10' foreground='gray'>Probably also work with other Linux distributions.</span>\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Alat ini harus digunakan dalam mode langsung dan untuk memulihkan boot Manjaro yang terinstal di hd "
"atau ssd.\n"
"\n"
"Jika sistem yang terinstal berjalan dengan benar, tidak ada masalah dalam boot, jadi lebih baik "
"tidak melanjutkan penggunaan alat ini.\n"
"\n"
"Mungkin juga bekerja dengan distribusi Linux lainnya.\n"
"\n"
"Apakah Anda ingin melanjutkan?"

msgid "Restore Boot, Grub, Initrd and others stuff"
msgstr "Taastage käivitus, grub, initrd ja muud asjad."

msgid "Wait..."
msgstr "Tunggu..."

msgid "I didn't find any Linux installed on this computer, canceled process.\n"
msgstr "Saya tidak menemukan sistem operasi Linux yang terpasang di komputer ini, proses dibatalkan."

msgid ""
"The boot in live mode is using EFI mode, but <span foreground='red'>I didn't find any EFI "
"partition</span> on this computer,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in Legacy or BIOS mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Støvelen i live-modus bruker efi-modus, men <span foreground='red'>jeg fant ingen "
"efi-partisjon</span> på denne datamaskinen,\n"
"sannsynligvis vil ikke grub restaurering fungere.\n"
"\n"
"prøv å starte på nytt og gjennom datamaskinens bios gjøre støvelen i legacy eller bios-modus.\n"
"\n"
"vil du prøve selv om det er lite sannsynlig at det vil fungere?"

msgid ""
"Boot in live mode is using Legacy mode, also called BIOS,\n"
"<span foreground='red'>but I found at least one EFI partition on this computer</span>,\n"
"probably GRUB restoration will not work.\n"
"\n"
"Try to restart and through the computer BIOS make the boot in EFI mode.\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to try even with little likely to work?"
msgstr ""
"Boot dalam mode langsung menggunakan mode warisan, juga disebut bios, tetapi saya menemukan "
"setidaknya satu partisi efi di komputer ini, kemungkinan pemulihan grub tidak akan berhasil.\n"
"\n"
"Coba restart dan melalui bios komputer membuat boot dalam mode efi.\n"
"\n"
"Apakah Anda ingin mencoba meskipun kemungkinan kecil untuk berhasil?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one EFI partition, select which one should use:"
msgstr ""
"Pilih opsi berikut ini:\n"
"\n"
"Saya menemukan lebih dari satu partisi EFI, pilih yang mana yang harus digunakan:"

msgid "No EFI partition selected, canceled process."
msgstr "Tiada bahagian efi yang dipilih, proses dibatalkan."

msgid "Restore the Boot, Grub and Initrd "
msgstr "Kembalikan boot, grub, dan initrd"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"\n"
"I found more than one Linux installed on this computer, select which one should restore the boot:"
msgstr ""
"Pilih opsi berikut ini:\n"
"\n"
"Saya menemukan lebih dari satu sistem operasi Linux yang terpasang di komputer ini, pilih yang mana "
"yang harus dipulihkan boot-nya:"

msgid "No selected partition, canceled process."
msgstr "Tiada bahagian yang dipilih, proses dibatalkan."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select an option:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"I found more than one storage device, select which one should record the boot:"
msgstr ""
"Pilih opsi berikut ini:\n"
"Saya menemukan lebih dari satu perangkat penyimpanan, pilih yang mana yang akan merekam boot:"

msgid "Disk"
msgstr "Diskijas"

msgid "Size"
msgstr "Stærð"

msgid "Name"
msgstr "Nafn"

msgid "Partition table"
msgstr "Tabel partisi"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>    \n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span>  LEGACY/BIOS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected disk:</span> $DISK_SELECTED\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk partition table:</span> $DISK_TABLE\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Disk Size:</span> $DISK_SIZE\n"
"   \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"Sahkan data ini:\n"
"\n"
"Mode boot:\n"
"warisan/BIOS\n"
"Disk terpilih: $disk_terpilih\n"
"\n"
"Jadual bahagian disk:\n"
"$jadual_disk\n"
"\n"
"Saiz disk:\n"
"$saiz_disk\n"
"\n"
"Bahagian terpilih:\n"
"$bahagian_terpilih\n"
"Sistem terpilih:\n"
"$os_terpilih\n"
"Format bahagian:\n"
"$format_bahagian\n"
"UUID bahagian:\n"
"$uuid_bahagian\n"
"\n"
"Adakah anda ingin meneruskan?"

msgid "Your computer is not connected to the internet, options 2 and 3 need internet to work."
msgstr "Komputer anda tidak terhubung ke internet, opsi 2 dan 3 memerlukan internet untuk berfungsi."

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways (<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or "
"Complete</span>),if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"Pilih pilihan yang diinginkan: pemulihan dapat dilakukan dalam 3 cara (sederhana, menengah, atau "
"lengkap), jika ragu, coba pilihan pertama, restart komputer dan lihat apakah masalah teratasi.\n"
"\n"
"Jika masalah masih berlanjut, coba pilihan lainnya."

msgid "Option"
msgstr "Pilihan"

msgid "Description"
msgstr "Kirjeldus"

msgid "Simple, just record the grub again at the beginning of the disk."
msgstr "Mudah, hanya rekam grub lagi di awal disk."

msgid ""
"Intermediate, reinstalls the GRUB package in the partition, generates the configuration and updates "
"Initrd."
msgstr ""
"Perantara, memasang semula pakej grub dalam bahagian, menghasilkan konfigurasi dan mengemaskini "
"initrd."

msgid ""
"Complete, performs the stages of the intermediate restoration, updates the system and checks if the "
"LTS kernel is installed."
msgstr ""
"Lengkap, melaksanakan tahap-tahap restorasi menengah, memperbarui sistem, dan memeriksa apakah "
"kernel lts terpasang."

msgid "Interactive, opens a terminal within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktif, membuka terminal di dalam sistem yang dipilih."

msgid "Interactive, opens a TUI control center within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktif, membuka pusat kontrol tui di dalam sistem yang dipilih."

msgid "Collect useful logs from installed system."
msgstr "Kumpulkan log yang berguna dari sistem yang terpasang."

msgid "Interactive, opens the package manager within the selected system."
msgstr "Interaktif, membuka pengelola paket di dalam sistem yang dipilih."

msgid "Restore System with Timeshift ( only if Timeshift is configurated )"
msgstr "Taastage süsteem koos timeshiftiga (ainult juhul, kui timeshift on konfigureeritud)."

msgid "Done!"
msgstr "Selesai!"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Confirm the data:</span>\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Boot mode:</span> EFI\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>EFI partition:</span> $EFI_PARTITION\n"
"    \n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected partition:</span> $SELECTED_PARTITION\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Selected system:</span> $SELECTED_OS\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition format:</span> $PARTITION_FORMAT\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>Partition UUID:</span> $UUID_PARTITION\n"
"\n"
"Do you want to proceed?"
msgstr ""
"<span font='16' foreground='lightskyblue'>kinnita andmed:</span>\n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>käivitusrežiim:</span> efi\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>efi partitsioon:</span> $efi_partitsioon\n"
"\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>valitud partitsioon:</span> $valitud_partitsioon\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>valitud süsteem:</span> $valitud_os\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>partitsiooni vorming:</span> $partitsiooni_vorming\n"
"<span font='11' foreground='gray'>partitsiooni uuid:</span> $uuid_partitsioon\n"
"\n"
"kas soovite jätkata?"

msgid ""
"<span font='16' foreground='LightSkyBlue'>Select the desired option:</span>\n"
"        \n"
"Restoration can be done in 3 ways(<span foreground='gray'>Simple, Intermediate or Complete</span>), "
"if in doubt, try the first\n"
"option, restart the computer and see if you resolved.\n"
"\n"
"If the problem persists try the other options."
msgstr ""
"Pilih opsi yang diinginkan: pemulihan dapat dilakukan dengan 3 cara (<span "
"foreground='gray'>sederhana, menengah, atau lengkap</span>), jika ragu, coba opsi pertama, restart "
"komputer dan lihat apakah masalah teratasi.\n"
"\n"
"Jika masalah masih berlanjut, coba opsi lainnya."

msgid "Timeshift not installed!"
msgstr "Timeshift tidak terpasang!"
